A timer/stopwatch plugin for gkrellm2.
Features:
* Timers and Stopwatches
* Multiple timers
* Continuous timers (restart on zero)
* Minimum space requirement
* Adjustable via mouse wheel
* Alarm via
  o Pop-Up window
  o Sound
  o External command
